Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:10.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:20.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}翌晨的阳光就快来临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:28.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}照进这间充满烟蒂 杂乱无章的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:38.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}Tell me why 圣母玛利亚 我对温柔感到饥渴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:48.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}Tell me why 为什么孤单的夜晚 总是如此漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:57.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}牛仔裤下的膝盖 被破碎的梦想打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:05.61,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}穿着衬衫的胸部太过耀眼 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠着开发电脑软件急速成长的 日和产业倒闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连带受到冲击的相关企业有 理参电器、轻井商事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及担商会 都被迫卷入连锁破产的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是今天的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师运气真背啊 明明好不容易找到工作了说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间“担商会”就是 你爸爸介绍给他的公司吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师现在可能打击太大 而卧床不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还上吊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师好可怜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#75 专一的爱情!八神和明日菜 是学不会教训的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐一脸闷闷不乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是为了五代的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,录用他的公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代的运气真的很背啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,有何贵干啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明天去探望一下 明日菜小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?明日菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次跟教练相亲的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚 听说她一直卧病不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去探望她一下 顺便去加深跟她的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,你烦不烦啊 我已经有喜欢的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才死脑筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人在哪里? 至少介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么企图?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那种女人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“那种女人”啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种好像酒桶穿着运动服的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在看谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说“酒桶穿着运动服” 他还真会形容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,的确是个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,去探望明日菜小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跟他们说好了 说你明天会去探望她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又自作主张了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了,我也会跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,等一等,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,真拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没跟相亲对象做个了断吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还没断清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,音无小姐请你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着这次的探望 我一定会跟她断得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不希望三鹰去做个了断吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你跟五代的感情 有所进展吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相亲对象的条件比我好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对三鹰也比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是蛮干脆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟五代之间到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么问 我们什么都没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出去啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,说不定会晚点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟阪本去喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要太消沈喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,反正公司到处都有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌,这么一点小事 我根本不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:06:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然强颜欢笑 但背影却看得出来在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那像从天堂被推入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪他会难过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛?怎么一副凶巴巴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把五代老师 介绍去快要倒闭的公司?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那件事啊 我没有想到那家公司会倒闭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就负起责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责?怎么负责?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮他介绍别的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的公司?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然罗 要不然五代老师太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也没有脸见他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再有本事 也无法再帮他的忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆,放洗澡水,我要洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,是叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬,我得先去个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己先去九条家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不在,事情比较好谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出去一下罗,麦肯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我已经克服怕狗的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用怕那个狗小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?三鹰先生要来的事 你还没跟明日菜说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,因为我对这门亲事 一直没什么兴致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为三鹰先生的女性关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为三鹰先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次来我们家都脸色发白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我倒是没听说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别让他跟明日菜见面好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从三鹰先生没来看她以后 明日菜就一直没有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会不会是得了相思病?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是三鹰的叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来访,请恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?三鹰的叔叔来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你找我有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就单刀直入的说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟阿瞬分手好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯答应 我一定会补偿你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…谈不上什么分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你也太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要给多少分手费?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一之濑太太! -一之濑太太!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰和我不是那种特别关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他向你求婚了,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,也仅止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算接受是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是阿瞬一厢情愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托,不要随便握她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真抱歉 这是我们家族的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来就圆满解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员真是挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连三鹰那么好的对象 她都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你的问题蛮多的 但你还是好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是三鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特洛贾诺夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一件,不,这一件…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉,三鹰先生 把你的西装弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么,请别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么没躲开呢? 还抱住迎面而来的圣伯纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦,不自觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,明日菜 你可以下床了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么切入主题呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子她一直没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这束花送给你,祝你康复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,好像没有必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没有必要哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我现在真的好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她难道真的是得了相思病吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,脸色突然变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你高兴成这个样子 害我不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴,好高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请三鹰先生来果然是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还是先不要谈好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的三鹰先生来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们都很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为明日菜生病不能陪它们玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前它们都无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来陪它们运动一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不必麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续陪他们聊下去的话 一定又会纠缠不清
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖,好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,要丢了,快去捡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生比以前有精神多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己爱瞎操心吧 他本来就很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,真的朝气蓬勃 而且很开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我自己进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的,我刚才去了 传闻中的寡妇那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寡妇没有那个意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖,好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,能不能请你 像以前一样来打工呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为暑假的关系 实习生都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在人手不足,真的很头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我还没找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 你尽管去找工作没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在的时候我会想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,待到找到新褓母为止就行了 好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且孩子们都等着你来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,这样真的好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的时期还去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,而且我已经答应他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人真的很不懂得拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优柔寡断的个性真的很吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,或许可以转换一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,就去转换一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你的下酒菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你怎么了? 表情好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,看起来很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是看起来好吃而已喔 你吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司…找到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹,我跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你到底打不打算去找公司?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么打不打算,我已经无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,五代老师怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代会怎么样都跟你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以说爸爸是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋就是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,笨蛋,笨蛋… 笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然变得好开朗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能见到孩子们的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连公司倒闭的打击都忘了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是五代的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是五代哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都过得好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖,好乖 今天起又可以跟你们一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,来,好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代肯回来 真的帮了我们一个大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且孩子们真的好喜欢他喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧,好高好高…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天要用什么手段 说服你爸爸呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么办法都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你什么都不做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们耳朵靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪小孩子玩真是累人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次家父给你带来很大的困扰 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家父为你找到下一个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且顺利就职之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在五代老师身边照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请各位,以及五代老师 多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,你太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,老师 晚饭已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,等一下,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,等一下,你听我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩真是学不会教训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓年轻的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下该怎么办呢?管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能顺其自然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:22:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还蛮看得开的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦,对啊 这是人家很努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,快点趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,老师,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,八神你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系,又没有人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没看到也听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,不要逃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要闹了!八神!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师,你的鼻子黏了饭粒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要这样啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生气罗!住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!三鹰拒绝了相亲对象?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还在众目睽睽的坟前…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要你答应嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下真的敲定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,不准他偷跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:24:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘我会等你的! 响子突然的含意深深宣言’
